    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ',' IN  L_AB WITH SPACE.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ',' IN  L_CR WITH SPACE.
    REPLACE ALL OCCURRENCES OF ',' IN  L_DR WITH SPACE.
